`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Earthquake
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast 'earthquake'

 This spell inflicts damage on every enemy character in the room. Be aware that
other characters who are not yet fighting may attack you as a result!

